ZH: 我已经用尽了所有的办法，但是问题还是没有解决。
EN: I have exhausted all the methods, but the problem is still not solved.

ZH: 她用尽了力气跑完了马拉松比赛。
EN: She exhausted all her strength and completed the marathon race.

ZH: 我们用尽了所有的时间才完成了这个项目。
EN: We used up all our time to complete this project.

ZH: 他用尽了所有的积蓄去旅行。
EN: He spent all his savings to travel.

ZH: 虽然他已经用尽了一切，但他决不放弃。
EN: Although he has used up everything, he will never give up.

ZH: 在这场战斗中，士兵们用尽了弹药。
EN: In this battle, the soldiers exhausted all their ammunition.

ZH: 她用尽了一切办法，终于买到了心仪已久的房子。
EN: She tried every possible means and finally bought the house she had longed for.

ZH: 这个团队用尽了所有的资源，希望能取得胜利。
EN: The team exhausted all their resources, hoping to achieve victory.

ZH: 我们在清理房间时用尽了一整天的时间。
EN: We spent the whole day cleaning the room.

ZH: 我用尽了所有的精力来完成这个任务。
EN: I exhausted all my energy to complete this task.

ZH: 她在买礼物时用尽了所有的存款。
EN: She used up all her savings to buy gifts.

ZH: 尽管我们用尽了一切，最终还是失败了。
EN: Despite our exhaustion of everything, we still failed in the end.

ZH: 他为了付清债务，用尽了所有的收入。
EN: He used up all his income to pay off the debts.

ZH: 我用尽了全部时间来准备这个演讲。
EN: I used up all my time to prepare for this speech.

ZH: 这个问题困扰了我很久，我用尽了所有的方法都无法解决。
EN: This problem has troubled me for a long time, and I have exhausted all the methods but cannot solve it.

ZH: 他用尽了全力打造出了一个成功的公司。
EN: He exerted all his efforts to create a successful company.

ZH: 这本书真的让我用尽了所有的情感。
EN: This book really drained all my emotions.

ZH: 我用尽了所有的油料做了一顿丰盛的晚餐。
EN: I used up all the cooking oil to make a sumptuous dinner.

ZH: 这场比赛他们用尽了所有的力气来争取胜利。
EN: In this game, they exerted all their strength to strive for victory.

ZH: 她为了照顾家庭用尽了一切，忽视了自己的健康。
EN: She exhausted everything to take care of her family and neglected her own health.
